<Layout title="What Drives Bitcoin's Price?" description="Understand the key factors that influence Bitcoin's price: supply and demand, halving events, institutional adoption, macroeconomics, and regulation." keywords="bitcoin price factors, what moves bitcoin, bitcoin supply demand, bitcoin halving price, institutional bitcoin, crypto market drivers">
